{
  "texts": [
    "Although there have been some studies on digital twins for elevators, the definition of digital twins remains somewhat ambiguous.",
    "Currently, the research on digital twins is just in its infancy, with few studies exploring the integration of elevator fault mechanisms with digital twins.",
    "However, combining fault numerical models with fault diagnosis methods can create a comprehensive digital twin model.",
    "This makes establishing a digital twin model for elevators the feasible direction to pursue.",
    "There is already a foundation for numerical modeling of elevators."
  ]
}